query:
SELECT vs.id, vs.shopNumber, c.name as centreName, fl.levelName
FROM vacant_shops vs
JOIN shopping_centres c ON vs.centreId = c.id
LEFT JOIN floor_levels fl ON vs.floorLevelId = fl.id
WHERE vs.mapMarkerX IS NULL OR vs.mapMarkerY IS NULL
LIMIT 10;
